window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A galaxy-conquering alien fleet is on Earth’s doorstep....</p> <p>A formidable alien armada stands on the brink of vanquishing the cosmos, their gaze set firmly on every inhabited world. The last line of defense? An eclectic crew of improbable champions: a maverick starfighter pilot, a daredevil stuntwoman, a lethal super-assassin, and a cosmic prankster with alien tricks up his sleeves. Their mission is to shield not just humanity, but billions of other intelligent lifeforms spanning the multiverse.</p> <p>Meet Jim, a quick-witted pilot grappling with OCD, who is planning to propose to his love when his life is disrupted by the sudden appearance of his blood-soaked friend, Kurt. This unexpected twist spirals Jim's life into a chaotic vortex of complicated problems, which include time travel and visits from alternate universes, with an impending galactic war threatening the very fabric of human existence at its core.</p> <p>Can this unlikely rag-tag group of heroes overcome their dysfunctions to shield first the galaxy and then the multiverse from the relentless onslaught of invincible alien forces?</p> <p>The Crimson Deathbringer series masterfully weaves nail-biting action scenes with wily humor, creating a riveting space opera saga. If you revel in immersive narratives like <i>Star Wars, Star Trek</i>, or <i>Stargate</i>, or if you're captivated by intense space battles, unforgettable characters, formidable foes, and unexpected, <i>Game of Thrones</i>-style plot twists, this series is penned expressly for you. Download today to embark on an adventure of galactic proportions!</p> <p>Also available in Spanish, Italian, German, and Greek!</p>"; 
